Extensive Re-ossification and Reformation of the Proximal Femur After External 
Beam Radiotherapy in Metastatic Carcinoma Breast.

Kharbanda Y(1), Singh R(2), Mir T(1), Tanwar YS(1).

Author information:
(1)1Department of Orthopedics, Apollo Hospital, HNo299, Pocket B, DDA Flats, 
Sarita Vihar, New Delhi, 110076 India.
